<H1 Style="color: BLUE;">FRONT APPROACHES </H1>
<p> TURN UNDERWATER+HEAD CARRY</p>
<img src="https://wallenswim.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wallen_Swim_On_Back-7.jpg"salt=Online Image" width="300">
<ul>
<li>Dive about one (1) meter
away from the victim. </li>
<li> Hold their legs to turn them
around</li>
<li>Lightly push their back
upwards in order for them to
float</li>
<li>Then, proceed to head carry</li>
</ul>
